headline: Is Chipotle (CMG) Pricing Reflect Its Brand Strength And Recent Share Price Pullback

The share price most recently closed at US$40.87, with returns of 2.3% over 7 days, 7.8% over 30 days, 9.0% year to date, and a 27.9% decline over the last year, alongside returns of 26.6% over 3 years and 38.1% over 5 years.
